title: Dutch Treat Portraits B061-065 (4 Top Dutch Women + Sia HQ)
description:
To be honest, I could not find a Fifth International Dutch Female Artist (with enough good material for showing off), I think, you should know. And every time, I look (and listen) to Sia, I see (and hear) something Dutch in her. All are singing in English anyway; so for me, she simply fits in.... Enjoy,
